{"type":"message","id":"42d51564","parentId":"7c85ea0b","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:39:17.005Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"杀号太狠了，遗漏杀号把几乎所有号码都杀了。这是因为30期数据中很多号码都有\"遗漏\"记录（因为总共只有30期，很多号码可能只出现1-2次）。\n\n需要调整一下遗漏杀号的阈值，让它更合理。让我修改杀号规则。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"遗漏杀号太狠了，需要调整阈值：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9vigi74vxtj9_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        # 前区遗漏超过 N 期（根据数据量动态调整）\n        # 数据少时提高阈值，避免误杀\n        threshold_front = max(10, len(history) // 2)  # 至少10期，最多数据量的一半\n        threshold_back = max(8, len(history) // 3)\n        \n        for ball, missing in front_missing.items():\n            if missing >= threshold_front:\n                killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        # 后区遗漏超过阈值\n        for ball, missing in back_missing.items():\n            if missing >= threshold_back:\n                killed_back.add(ball)\n        \n        result = KillResult(\n            rule_name=\"遗漏杀号\",\n            killed_front=killed_front,\n            killed_back=killed_back,\n            reason=f\"前区遗漏≥{threshold_front}期({len(killed_front)}个) + 后区遗漏≥{threshold_back}期({len(killed_back)}个)\"\n        )","oldText":"        # 前区遗漏超过15期\n        for ball, missing in front_missing.items():\n            if missing >= 15:\n                killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        # 后区遗漏超过10期\n        for ball, missing in back_missing.items():\n            if missing >= 10:\n                killed_back.add(ball)\n        \n        result = KillResult(\n            rule_name=\"遗漏杀号\",\n            killed_front=killed_front,\n            killed_back=killed_back,\n            reason=f\"前区遗漏≥15期({len(killed_front)}个) + 后区遗漏≥10期({len(killed_back)}个)\"\n        )"}],"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/kill_rules.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":82984,"output":570,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWr