{"type":"message","id":"9df21a4b","parentId":"0a23492c","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:39:51.307Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"遗漏杀号还是太强了。问题是30期数据中，大多数号码都出现过1-2次，所以\"遗漏\"值实际上是：总期数 - 出现位置。而不是我们想要的\"连续遗漏\"。\n\n我需要重新设计遗漏杀号的逻辑。应该统计的是每个号码\"最近一次出现是在多少期之前\"，而不是\"出现了多少次\"。\n\n让我重新检查统计逻辑。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"遗漏杀号逻辑有问题，需要修复——应该是\"最近一期距今多少期没出\"，而不是\"出现次数\"。让我重新实现：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ai2385qybxh8_1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":85,"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/data_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":3149,"output":250,"cacheRead":82875,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86274,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778413183009,"responseId":"064fa17f572e37e4bbbd8fdbd1d55f58"}}
{"type":"message","id":"349adc77","parentId":"9df21a4b","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:39:51.311Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ai2385qybxh8_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def get_latest_update_time(self) -> Optional[datetime]:\n        \"\"\"获取最新数据的更新时间\"\"\"\n        conn = self.get_connection()\n        cursor = conn.cursor()\n        cursor.execute('SELECT MAX(updated_at) FROM lottery_records')\n        result = cursor.fetchone()[0]\n        conn.close()\n        if result:\n            return datetime.fromisoformat(result)\n        return None\n    \n    def is_fresh(self, hours: int = 48) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"检查数据是否新鲜\"\"\"\n        update_time = self.get_latest_update_time()\n        if not update_time:\n            return False\n        return datetime.now() - update_time < timedelta(hours=hours)\n    \n    def need_more_data(self, required: int = 100) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"检查是否需要更多数据\"\"\"\n        return self.get_count() < required\n    \n    def get_statistics(self, history: List[dict]) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"\n        计算统计数据\n        \n        Args:\n            history: 历史数据列表\n            \n        Returns:\n            dict: 包含频率、遗漏等统计信息\n        \"\"\"\n        # 初始化前区统计（1-35）\n        front_count = {i: 0 for i in range(1, 36)}\n        back_count = {i: 0 for i in range(1, 13)}\n        \n        # 初始化前区遗漏（1-35）\n        front_missing = {i: len(history) for i in range(1, 36)}\n        back_missing = {i: len(history) for i in range(1, 13)}\n        \n        # 遍历历史数据更新统计\n        for idx, record in enumerate(history):\n            # 前区\n            for ball in record['front']:\n                front_count[ball] += 1\n                if front_missing[ball] == len(history):\n                    front_missing[ball] = len(history) - idx - 1\n            \n            # 后区\n            for ball in record['back']:\n                back_count[ball] += 1\n                if back_missing[ball] == len(history):\n                    back_missing[ball] = len(history) - idx - 1\n        \n        # 计算尾数统计\n        tail_count = {i: 0 for i in range(10)}\n        for ball in range(1, 36):\n            tail_count[ball % 10] += front_count[ball]\n        \n        # 获取各区出号情况（7区划分）\n        zones = self._get_zone_distribution(history)\n        \n        return {\n            'front_count': front_count,\n            'back_count': back_count,\n            'front_missing': front_missing,\n            'back_missing': back_missing,\n            'tail_count': tail_count,\n            'zones': zones,\n            'total': len(history)\n        }\n    \n    def _get_zone_distribution(self, history: List[dict]) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"\n        计算区间分布\n        7区划分: 01-05, 06-10, 11-15, 16-20, 21-25, 26-30, 31-35\n        \"\"\"\n        zones = {i: [] for i in range(1, 8)}  # 7个区\n        \n        for record in history:\n\n[64 more lines in file. Use offset=165 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778413191311}}
{"type":"message","id":"ced84b32","parentId":"349adc77","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:40:16.180Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了问题。遗漏统计的逻辑是正确的：`front_missing[ball] = len(history) - idx - 1` 应该记录的是\"从当前位置到该球出现时的距离\"。\n\n但实际上这个逻辑有问题——它只记录了最后一次出现的位置，而不是正确的\"当前遗漏\"。\n\n正确的遗漏计算应该是：\n- 对于每个球，找到它在历史数据中最后一次出现的位置\n- 遗漏 = 当前期数 - 最后一次出现的位置\n\n让我修复这个问题。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gl2sadulxzvh_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    def get_statistics(self, history: List[dict]) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"\n        计算统计数据\n        \n        Args:\n            history: 历史数据列表（按期号降序，最新在前）\n            \n        Returns:\n            dict: 包含频率、遗漏等统计信息\n        \"\"\"\n        # 初始化前区统计（1-35）\n        front_count = {i: 0 for i in range(1, 36)}\n        back_count = {i: 0 for i in range(1, 13)}\n        \n        # 初始化前区遗漏（1-35）- 表示该球从\"最后一次出现\"距今多少期\n        front_missing = {i: len(history) for i in range(1, 36)}\n        back_missing = {i: len(history) for i in range(1, 13)}\n        \n        # 遍历历史数据更新统计\n        for idx, record in enumerate(history):\n            # 前区\n            for ball in record['front']:\n                front_count[ball] += 1\n                # 只更新\"第一次出现\"的距离（后续出现会被忽略，保持最大的遗漏值）\n                # 实际上要记录的是\"当前遗漏\"，即最后一次出现距今多少期\n                # 由于是按降序遍历，idx=0是最新，所以遗漏应该是 idx\n                # 但这里我们想要的是\"从最后一次出现到现在隔了多少期\"\n                if front_count[ball] == 1:  # 第一次出现时记录\n                    front_missing[ball] = idx\n            \n            # 后区\n            for ball in record['back']:\n                back_count[ball] += 1\n                if back_count[ball] == 1:\n                    back_missing[ball] = idx\n        \n        # 修正遗漏值：把\"第一次出现的位置\"改为\"最后一次出现的位置\"\n        # 需要反向遍历来找最后一次出现\n        front_last_appear = {i: -1 for i in range(1, 36)}\n        back_last_appear = {i: -1 for i in range(1, 13)}\n        \n        for idx, record in enumerate(history):\n            for ball in record['front']:\n                front_last_appear[ball] = idx\n            for ball in record['back']:\n                back_last_appear[ball] = idx\n        \n        # 正确遗漏 = 当前索引(0) - 最后一次出现的位置\n        for ball in range(1, 36):\n            if front_last_appear[ball] >= 0:\n                front_missing[ball] = front_last_appear[ball]\n            else:\n                front_missing[ball] = len(history)\n        \n        for ball in range(1, 13):\n            if back_last_appear[ball] >= 0:\n                back_missing[ball] = back_last_appear[ball]\n            else:\n                back_missing[ball] = len(history)\n        \n        # 计算尾数统计\n        tail_count = {i: 0 for i in range(10)}\n        for ball in range(1, 36):\n            tail_count[ball % 10] += front_count[ball]\n        \n        # 获取各区出号情况（7区划分）\n        zones = self._get_zone_distribution(history)\n        \n        return {\n            'front_count': front_count,\n            'back_count': back_count,\n            'front_missing': front_missing,\n            'back_missing': back_missing,\n            'tail_count': tail_count,\n            'zones': zones,\n            'total': len(history)\n        }","oldText":"    def get_statistics(self, history: List[dict]) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"\n        计算统计数据\n        \n        Args:\n            history: 历史数据列表\n            \n        Returns:\n            dict: 包含频率、遗漏等统计信息\n        \"\"\"\n        # 初始化前区统计（1-35）\n        front_count = {i: 0 for i in range(1, 36)}\n        back_count = {i: 0 for i in range(1, 13)}\n        \n        # 初始化前区遗漏（1-35）\n        front_missing = {i: len(history) for i in range(1, 36)}\n        back_missing = {i: len(history) for i in range(1, 13)}\n        \n        # 遍历历史数据更新统计\n        for idx, record in enumerate(history):\n            # 前区\n            for ball in record['front']:\n                front_count[ball] += 1\n                if front_missing[ball] == len(history):\n                    front_missing[ball] = len(history) - idx - 1\n            \n            # 后区\n            for ball in record['back']:\n                back_count[ball] += 1\n                if back_missing[ball] == len(history):\n                    back_missing[ball] = len(history) - idx - 1\n        \n        # 计算尾数统计\n        tail_count = {i: 0 for i in range(10)}\n        for ball in range(1, 36):\n            tail_count[ball % 10] += front_count[ball]\n        \n        # 获取各区出号情况（7区划分）\n        zones = self._get_zone_distribution(history)\n        \n        return {\n            'front_count': front_count,\n            'back_count': back_count,\n            'front_missing': front_missing,\n            'back_missing': back_missing,\n            'tail_count': tail_count,\n            'zones': zones,\n            'total': len(history)\n        }"}],"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/data_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":883,"output":1543,"cacheRead":86011,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88437,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778413191313,"responseId":"064fa1877cecf81277d425ce08d13d0e"}}
