{"type":"message","id":"3e56a6a3","parentId":"099ac777","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:40:42.124Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"实际上，我上面的逻辑还是有问题。正确的\"遗漏\"应该是：\n\n- 对于已经出现的号码：遗漏 = 当前位置（因为最新的是0，上一期是1...）\n- 对于没有出现的号码：遗漏 = 总期数\n\n但这样还是不对。让我重新思考一下：\n\n历史数据是按期号降序的：\n- idx=0: 最新一期 (26050)\n- idx=1: 上一期 (26049)\n- ...\n- idx=n-1: 最早的\n\n\"遗漏\"的正确含义应该是：该号码从最后一次出现到现在，隔了多少期。\n\n如果一个号码在 idx=5 出现过，那么它的遗漏就是 5（表示从那之后已经过了5期）。\n\n让我重新修正这个逻辑。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_y62j3g6ivcx0_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    def get_statistics(self, history: List[dict]) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"\n        计算统计数据\n        \n        Args:\n            history: 历史数据列表（按期号降序，最新在前）\n            \n        Returns:\n            dict: 包含频率、遗漏等统计信息\n        \"\"\"\n        total = len(history)\n        \n        # 初始化前区统计（1-35）\n        front_count = {i: 0 for i in range(1, 36)}\n        back_count = {i: 0 for i in range(1, 13)}\n        \n        # 初始化遗漏 = 总期数（表示从未出现）\n        front_missing = {i: total for i in range(1, 36)}\n        back_missing = {i: total for i in range(1, 13)}\n        \n        # 遍历历史数据：idx=0是最新，idx越大越老\n        for idx, record in enumerate(history):\n            for ball in record['front']:\n                front_count[ball] += 1\n                # 遗漏 = 该球最后一次出现时的索引（最小的索引=最新的出现）\n                # 因为按降序排列，idx越小越新\n                # 所以遗漏 = idx（从最后一次出现到现在隔了多少期）\n                if front_missing[ball] == total:  # 第一次处理这个球\n                    front_missing[ball] = idx\n            \n            for ball in record['back']:\n                back_count[ball] += 1\n                if back_missing[ball] == total:\n                    back_missing[ball] = idx\n        \n        # 计算尾数统计\n        tail_count = {i: 0 for i in range(10)}\n        for ball in range(1, 36):\n            tail_count[ball % 10] += front_count[ball]\n        \n        # 获取各区出号情况（7区划分）\n        zones = self._get_zone_distribution(history)\n        \n        return {\n            'front_count': front_count,\n            'back_count': back_count,\n            'front_missing': front_missing,\n            'back_missing': back_missing,\n            'tail_count': tail_count,\n            'zones': zones,\n            'total': total\n        }","oldText":"    def get_statistics(self, history: List[dict]) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"\n        计算统计数据\n        \n        Args:\n            history: 历史数据列表（按期号降序，最新在前）\n            \n        Returns:\n            dict: 包含频率、遗漏等统计信息\n        \"\"\"\n        # 初始化前区统计（1-35）\n        front_count = {i: 0 for i in range(1, 36)}\n        back_count = {i: 0 for i in range(1, 13)}\n        \n        # 初始化前区遗漏（1-35）- 表示该球从\"最后一次出现\"距今多少期\n        front_missing = {i: len(history) for i in range(1, 36)}\n        back_missing = {i: len(history) for i in range(1, 13)}\n        \n        # 遍历历史数据更新统计\n        for idx, record in enumerate(history):\n            # 前区\n            for ball in record['front']:\n                front_count[ball] += 1\n                # 只更新\"第一次出现\"的距离（后续出现会被忽略，保持最大的遗漏值）\n                # 实际上要记录的是\"当前遗漏\"，即最后一次出现距今多少期\n                # 由于是按降序遍历，idx=0是最新，所以遗漏应该是 idx\n                # 但这里我们想要的是\"从最后一次出现到现在隔了多少期\"\n                if front_count[ball] == 1:  # 第一次出现时记录\n                    front_missing[ball] = idx\n            \n            # 后区\n            for ball in record['back']:\n                back_count[ball] += 1\n                if back_count[ball] == 1:\n                    back_missing[ball] = idx\n        \n        # 修正遗漏值：把\"第一次出现的位置\"改为\"最后一次出现的位置\"\n        # 需要反向遍历来找最后一次出现\n        front_last_appear = {i: -1 for i in range(1, 36)}\n        back_last_appear = {i: -1 for i in range(1, 13)}\n        \n        for idx, record in enumerate(history):\n            for ball in record['front']:\n                front_last_appear[ball] = idx\n            for ball in record['back']:\n                back_last_appear[ball] = idx\n        \n        # 正确遗漏 = 当前索引(0) - 最后一次出现的位置\n        for ball in range(1, 36):\n            if front_last_appear[ball] >= 0:\n                front_missing[ball] = front_last_appear[ball]\n            else:\n                front_missing[ball] = len(history)\n        \n        for ball in range(1, 13):\n            if back_last_appear[ball] >= 0:\n                back_missing[ball] = back_last_appear[ball]\n            else:\n                back_missing[ball] = len(history)\n        \n        # 计算尾数统计\n        tail_count = {i: 0 for i in range(10)}\n        for ball in range(1, 36):\n            tail_count[ball % 10] += front_count[ball]\n        \n        # 获取各区出号情况（7区划分）\n        zones = self._get_zone_distribution(history)\n        \n        return {\n            'front_count': front_count,\n            'back_count': back_count,\n            'front_missing': front_missing,\n            'back_missing': back_missing,\n            'tail_count': tail_count,\n            'zones': zones,\n            'total': len(history)\n        }"}],"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/data_manager.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":131,"output":1704,"cacheRead":88251,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90086,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778413216190,"responseId":"064fa1a0eb6e294107f064394625d64e"}}
