{"type":"message","id":"8bf737e2","parentId":"a1205658","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:41:10.057Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_fi6yxvbwn8a8_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/backtest.py\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/data_manager.py\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/__init__.py\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/kill_rules.py\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/predict_after_kill.py\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/report.py\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/main.py\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/SKILL.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9,"aggregated":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/backtest.py\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/data_manager.py\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/__init__.py\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/kill_rules.py\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/predict_after_kill.py\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/report.py\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/main.py\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/SKILL.md","cwd":"/workspace/projects/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778413270057}}
{"type":"message","id":"e676a64a","parentId":"8bf737e2","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:41:21.077Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"技能开发完成！让我给用户一个总结。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **大乐透杀号选球技能开发完成！**\n\n---\n\n## 📁 文件结构\n\n```\nsuper-lotto-killer/\n├── SKILL.md                    # 技能说明文档\n├── main.py                     # 主入口\n└── killer/\n    ├── __init__.py\n    ├── data_manager.py         # 数据管理（本地优先）\n    ├── kill_rules.py           # 8种杀号规则\n    ├── predict_after_kill.py   # 杀号后预测\n    ├── backtest.py             # 回测验证\n    └── report.py               # 报告生成\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🔪 实现的8种杀号规则\n\n| # | 规则 | 逻辑 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | 冷热号杀号 | 频率>均值2.5倍的热号 + 最低3个冷号 |\n| 2 | 遗漏值杀号 | 前区遗漏≥15期、后区≥8期（动态调整） |\n| 3 | 尾数杀号 | 热尾（>均值1.5倍）+ 冷尾（连续5期未出） |\n| 4 | 断区杀号 | 7区出号密度极低的区间 |\n| 5 | 加减法杀号 | 相邻差 +3/-3运算 |\n| 6 | 公式杀号 | 三种经典公式 |\n| 7 | 首尾联动 | (最小前区+最大后区)%35 |\n| 8 | 和值杀号 | 近10期和值趋势 |\n\n---\n\n## 📊 回测结果（基于30期数据）\n\n- **前区准确率**: 87.3%（杀的号码中87%确实没中）\n- **平均每期杀**: 前区19.5个，后区1.7个\n- **命中率**: 前区平均杀中2.46个/期\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 使用方法\n\n```bash\n# 完整杀号预测（默认3组）\npython main.py\n\n# 指定分析期数和预测组数\npython main.py --history 50 --count 5\n\n# 回测验证\npython main.py --backtest\n\n# 查看规则说明\npython main.py --rules\n```\n\n数据源优先从本地数据库读取，复用 super-lotto 技能的数据！🍀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":334,"output":508,"cacheRead":93179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94021,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778413270058,"responseId":"064fa1d6ef4bd42e5aa9796466645c28"}}
