{"type":"message","id":"ac8dfa52","parentId":"2571a02a","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:46:26.528Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"网站确实只能显示最近的数据。这可能是网站的设计限制。不过这对于杀号技能来说，30-50期数据应该已经足够进行分析了。\n\n让我总结一下数据情况给用户：\n1. 本地数据库：32期数据（26019-26050）\n2. 网站限制：只能获取最近约32期数据\n3. 这对于杀号统计分析来说，数据量已经足够\n\n但如果用户需要更完整的历史数据，可能需要找其他数据源或者API。让我给用户一个完整的总结。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"根据检查，发现以下情况：\n\n## 📊 数据完整性检查结果\n\n| 来源 | 数据范围 | 记录数 |\n|------|----------|--------|\n| **本地数据库** | 26019期 ~ 26050期 | **32期** |\n| **网站限制** | 约32期 | 无法获取更多 |\n\n### 网站限制说明\n\n彩票500万网站默认只显示**最近32期**数据，无论点击\"最近30期/50期/100期\"还是手动输入期号范围，都只能获取约32期记录。\n\n### 当前数据状态\n\n```\n✅ 最新期: 26050期 (2026-05-09)\n✅ 最早期: 26019期 (2026-03-02)\n⏰ 数据跨度: 约2个月\n📈 数据量: 32期\n```\n\n### 对杀号技能的影响\n\n**✅ 32期数据足够进行统计分析**\n\n对于杀号规则来说：\n- 冷热号统计：✅ 足够\n- 遗漏值追踪：✅ 足够\n- 尾数分析：✅ 足够\n- 断区分析：✅ 足够\n\n### 如需更完整历史数据\n\n可以尝试以下方式：\n1. **其他数据源**：如 百度彩票、网易彩票 等可能有更完整历史\n2. **API接口**：彩票官方可能有API\n3. **手动补充**：如果知道特定期号的开奖结果，可以手动录入\n\n需要我帮你探索其他数据源吗？🍀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":420,"output":523,"cacheRead":99899,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100842,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778413571534,"responseId":"064fa3042e5ba510a4fba90bfbc748c0"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6eecdeac","parentId":"ac8dfa52","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:49:30.947Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f334258e8a4c4eaa801c6e326d\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"sender\": \"haidong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-05-10 19:49 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b6f334258e8a4c4eaa801c6e326d]\nhaidong: 前区杀号的准确率还不到百分之九十五，需要再次优化算法，提升杀号准确率！"}],"timestamp":1778413770943}}
{"type":"message","id":"d434e551","parentId":"6eecdeac","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:49:50.966Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说前区杀号准确率不到95%，需要优化算法提升准确率。\n\n回测结果显示：\n- 前区准确率: 87.3%\n- 前区平均命中: 2.46 个/期\n\n用户希望准确率提升到95%以上。\n\n让我分析一下如何提升：\n\n1. **当前问题**：平均每期杀中2.46个开奖号码，意味着杀的24个号码中约有2.46个是实际开奖号码\n2. **目标**：杀掉的号码尽量不要出现在开奖结果中\n\n优化方向：\n1. **降低杀号数量**：不要杀太多号码，留有余地\n2. **提高杀号门槛**：只有多个规则同时命中的才杀掉\n3. **改进冷热号逻辑**：热号不一定降温，冷号可能回补\n4. **加入更多验证**：只有统计意义上显著的才杀\n5. **限制单规则杀号**：单规则命中的号码降低杀号权重\n\n让我重新设计杀号策略：\n\n1. **高置信度杀号**（≥2规则）：这些是主要杀号对象\n2. **单规则杀号**：降低权重，只有特别极端的情况才杀\n3. **保守冷热杀号**：不要杀太多热号，因为热号可能继续热\n4. **遗漏值动态调整**：根据数据量调整阈值\n\n\n5. **尾数杀号保守处理**：尾数规律不稳定，需要谨慎对待\n6. **和值杀号精细化**：缩小和值范围以减少误杀\n\n关键是调整策略：杀号数量控制在10-15个（目前24个太多），同时提高每个杀号决定的置信度，只有多个规则同时指向时才真正杀掉。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，让我分析回测数据并优化杀号算法。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_opum1e5d27rc_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer && python -c '\nfrom killer.data_manager import DataManager\nfrom killer.kill_rules import KillRuleEngine\nfrom killer.backtest import BacktestEngine\n\ndm = DataManager()\nhistory = dm.get_history(30)\nstats = dm.get_statistics(history)\n\n# 详细分析各规则的杀号效果\nprint(\"=\" * 60)\nprint(\"各规则杀号数量统计\")\nprint(\"=\" * 60)\n\nengine = KillRuleEngine(history, stats)\nresults = engine.run_all()\n\nfor r in results:\n    print(f\"{r.rule_name}: 前区 {len(r.killed_front)}个, 后区 {len(r.killed_back)}个\")\n\nprint()\nprint(\"=\" * 60)\nprint(\"被杀号码的频率分布分析\")\nprint(\"=\" * 60)\n\nkilled_front, killed_back = engine.get_all_killed()\nfor ball in sorted(killed_front)[:20]:\n    count = stats[\"front_count\"][ball]\n    missing = stats[\"front_missing\"][ball]\n    print(f\"{ball:02d}号: 出现{count}次, 遗漏{missing}期\")\n'","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":100200,"output":993,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101193,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778413770947,"responseId":"064fa3cbe0276410edf81f0f3a342c4c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a894e956","parentId":"d434e551","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:49:51.019Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_opum1e5d27rc_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"============================================================\n各规则杀号数量统计\n============================================================\n冷热杀号: 前区 3个, 后区 0个\n遗漏杀号: 前区 3个, 后区 2个\n尾数杀号: 前区 4个, 后区 0个\n断区杀号: 前区 0个, 后区 0个\n加减法: 前区 12个, 后区 0个\n公式杀号: 前区 8个, 后区 0个\n首尾联动: 前区 1个, 后区 0个\n和值杀号: 前区 0个, 后区 0个\n\n============================================================\n被杀号码的频率分布分析\n============================================================\n01号: 出现3次, 遗漏1期\n02号: 出现4次, 遗漏8期\n03号: 出现5次, 遗漏6期\n04号: 出现3次, 遗漏14期\n05号: 出现4次, 遗漏17期\n07号: 出现4次, 遗漏8期\n08号: 出现6次, 遗漏6期\n09号: 出现6次, 遗漏3期\n10号: 出现5次, 遗漏0期\n11号: 出现5次, 遗漏2期\n12号: 出现6次, 遗漏7期\n13号: 出现5次, 遗漏4期\n14号: 出现4次, 遗漏0期\n16号: 出现2次, 遗漏14期\n17号: 出现5次, 遗漏1期\n19号: 出现3次, 遗漏7期\n20号: 出现3次, 遗漏2期\n22号: 出现6次, 遗漏6期\n23号: 出现3次, 遗漏0期\n26号: 出现9次, 遗漏5期"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":46,"aggregated":"============================================================\n各规则杀号数量统计\n============================================================\n冷热杀号: 前区 3个, 后区 0个\n遗漏杀号: 前区 3个, 后区 2个\n尾数杀号: 前区 4个, 后区 0个\n断区杀号: 前区 0个, 后区 0个\n加减法: 前区 12个, 后区 0个\n公式杀号: 前区 8个, 后区 0个\n首尾联动: 前区 1个, 后区 0个\n和值杀号: 前区 0个, 后区 0个\n\n============================================================\n被杀号码的频率分布分析\n============================================================\n01号: 出现3次, 遗漏1期\n02号: 出现4次, 遗漏8期\n03号: 出现5次, 遗漏6期\n04号: 出现3次, 遗漏14期\n05号: 出现4次, 遗漏17期\n07号: 出现4次, 遗漏8期\n08号: 出现6次, 遗漏6期\n09号: 出现6次, 遗漏3期\n10号: 出现5次, 遗漏0期\n11号: 出现5次, 遗漏2期\n12号: 出现6次, 遗漏7期\n13号: 出现5次, 遗漏4期\n14号: 出现4次, 遗漏0期\n16号: 出现2次, 遗漏14期\n17号: 出现5次, 遗漏1期\n19号: 出现3次, 遗漏7期\n20号: 出现3次, 遗漏2期\n22号: 出现6次, 遗漏6期\n23号: 出现3次, 遗漏0期\n26号: 出现9次, 遗漏5期","cwd":"/workspace/projects/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778413791019}}
{"type":"message","id":"5cbc2207","parentId":"a894e956","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:50:00.607Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到问题了！被杀掉的号码中有很多是：\n1. 出现次数较高的号码（如26号出现9次）\n2. 遗漏很低的号码（如10号、14号、23号遗漏0期，说明上期刚出）\n\n这说明：\n1. **加减法杀号杀太多了**：12个，很多是上期刚出的号码\n2. **公式杀号也有问题**：包括了很多遗漏0的号码\n3. **冷热杀号过于激进**：杀了热号26\n\n优化方向：\n1. **去除上期刚出的号码**：遗漏0的号码不要杀\n2. **限制加减法杀号**：不要把上期号码参与运算后杀掉\n3. **冷热杀号保守**：只杀极端冷号，不杀热号\n4. **提高阈值**：遗漏值要更高才杀\n5. **只有高置信度才杀**：单规则命中的号码要更严格的阈值\n\n让我重新设计杀号逻辑。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"问题找到了！被杀掉的号码中很多遗漏为0（上期刚出），需要大幅优化：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sa5xzdouety2_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/kill_rules.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":477,"output":471,"cacheRead":100795,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101743,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778413791021,"responseId":"064fa3df9e46346e1ff7c74c7fd4d582"}}
{"type":"message","id":"eb3e9aa8","parentId":"5cbc2207","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:50:00.612Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_sa5xzdouety2_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\n大乐透杀号选球技能 - 杀号规则引擎\n实现8种杀号规则\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom typing import List, Set, Dict, Tuple\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass, field\nfrom killer.data_manager import DataManager, DataManager\n\n\n@dataclass\nclass KillResult:\n    \"\"\"杀号结果\"\"\"\n    rule_name: str\n    killed_front: Set[int] = field(default_factory=set)\n    killed_back: Set[int] = field(default_factory=set)\n    reason: str = \"\"\n    confidence: str = \"normal\"  # normal / high\n\n\nclass KillRuleEngine:\n    \"\"\"杀号规则引擎\"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, history: List[dict], stats: dict = None):\n        self.history = history\n        self.latest = history[0] if history else None\n        self.stats = stats\n        self.results: List[KillResult] = []\n        self.dm = DataManager()\n    \n    def run_all(self) -> List[KillResult]:\n        \"\"\"执行所有杀号规则\"\"\"\n        # 确保有统计数据\n        if not self.stats:\n            self.stats = self.dm.get_statistics(self.history)\n        \n        self.results = []\n        \n        # 1. 冷热号杀号\n        self._kill_by_cold_hot()\n        \n        # 2. 遗漏值杀号\n        self._kill_by_missing()\n        \n        # 3. 尾数杀号\n        self._kill_by_tail()\n        \n        # 4. 断区杀号\n        self._kill_by_zone()\n        \n        # 5. 加减法杀号\n        self._kill_by_addsub()\n        \n        # 6. 公式杀号\n        self._kill_by_formula()\n        \n        # 7. 首尾联动\n        self._kill_by_head_tail()\n        \n        # 8. 和值杀号\n        self._kill_by_sum()\n        \n        return self.results\n    \n    def _kill_by_cold_hot(self):\n        \"\"\"冷热号杀号 - 基于频率统计\"\"\"\n        front_count = self.stats['front_count']\n        back_count = self.stats['back_count']\n        total = self.stats['total']\n        \n        # 计算平均频率\n        front_avg = sum(front_count.values()) / 35\n        back_avg = sum(back_count.values()) / 12\n        \n        killed_front = set()\n        killed_back = set()\n        \n        # 热号（超过平均值2.5倍）杀掉 - 适度调高避免误杀\n        hot_count = 0\n        for ball, count in front_count.items():\n            if count >= front_avg * 2.5:\n                killed_front.add(ball)\n                hot_count += 1\n        \n        # 冷号（频率最低的前3个）杀掉\n        sorted_front = sorted(front_count.items(), key=lambda x: x[1])\n        for ball, _ in sorted_front[:3]:\n            killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        # 后区热号（超过平均值2倍）杀掉\n        for ball, count in back_count.items():\n            if count >= back_avg * 2:\n                killed_back.add(ball)\n        \n        result = KillResult(\n            rule_name=\"冷热杀号\",\n            killed_front=killed_front,\n            killed_back=killed_back,\n            reason=f\"热号({hot_count}个, ≥均值2.5倍) + 冷号(最低3个)\"\n        )\n        self.results.append(result)\n    \n    def _kill_by_missing(self):\n        \"\"\"遗漏值杀号 - 追踪号码遗漏周期\"\"\"\n        front_missing = self.stats['front_missing']\n        back_missing = self.stats['back_missing']\n        \n        killed_front = set()\n        killed_back = set()\n        \n        # 前区遗漏超过 N 期（根据数据量动态调整）\n        # 数据少时提高阈值，避免误杀\n        threshold_front = max(10, len(self.history) // 2)  # 至少10期，最多数据量的一半\n        threshold_back = max(8, len(self.history) // 3)\n        \n        for ball, missing in front_missing.items():\n            if missing >= threshold_front:\n                killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        # 后区遗漏超过阈值\n        for ball, missing in back_missing.items():\n            if missing >= threshold_back:\n                killed_back.add(ball)\n        \n        result = KillResult(\n            rule_name=\"遗漏杀号\",\n            killed_front=killed_front,\n            killed_back=killed_back,\n            reason=f\"前区遗漏≥{threshold_front}期({len(killed_front)}个) + 后区遗漏≥{threshold_back}期({len(killed_back)}个)\"\n        )\n        self.results.append(result)\n    \n    def _kill_by_tail(self):\n        \"\"\"尾数杀号 - 基于尾数统计\"\"\"\n        total = self.stats['total']\n        killed_front = set()\n        \n        # 统计各尾数出现次数\n        tail_appear = {i: 0 for i in range(10)}\n        for ball in range(1, 36):\n            tail_appear[ball % 10] += self.stats['front_count'][ball]\n        \n        # 计算每个尾数平均出现次数\n        avg_per_tail = total * 5 / 10  # 每期5个前区，10个尾数\n        \n        # 热尾（出现次数远超平均）杀掉\n        for tail in range(10):\n            if tail_appear[tail] >= avg_per_tail * 1.5:\n                # 该尾数的所有号码杀掉\n                for ball in range(1, 36):\n                    if ball % 10 == tail:\n                        killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        # 冷尾（连续5期未出现）\n        recent_tails = self.dm.get_recent_tails(self.history, 5)\n        for tail, appears in recent_tails.items():\n            if sum(appears) == 0:  # 连续5期未出现\n                for ball in range(1, 36):\n                    if ball % 10 == tail:\n                        killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        result = KillResult(\n            rule_name=\"尾数杀号\",\n            killed_front=killed_front,\n            killed_back=set(),\n            reason=f\"热尾({len([t for t in tail_appear if t >= avg_per_tail*1.5])}) + 冷尾\"\n        )\n        self.results.append(result)\n    \n    def _kill_by_zone(self):\n        \"\"\"断区杀号 - 区间分布分析\"\"\"\n        zones = self.stats['zones']\n        killed_front = set()\n        \n        # 7区: 01-05, 06-10, 11-15, 16-20, 21-25, 26-30, 31-35\n        zone_names = {\n            1: \"01-05\", 2: \"06-10\", 3: \"11-15\", 4: \"16-20\",\n            5: \"21-25\", 6: \"26-30\", 7: \"31-35\"\n        }\n        \n        # 检查每个区的出号密度\n        for zone_id, balls in zones.items():\n            if len(balls) == 0:\n                # 该区最近N期没有出号，整个区杀掉\n                for ball in range((zone_id-1)*5+1, zone_id*5+1):\n                    if 1 <= ball <= 35:\n                        killed_front.add(ball)\n            elif len(balls) < self.stats['total'] * 0.05:\n                # 出号密度极低\n                for ball in range((zone_id-1)*5+1, zone_id*5+1):\n                    if 1 <= ball <= 35:\n                        killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        result = KillResult(\n            rule_name=\"断区杀号\",\n            killed_front=killed_front,\n            killed_back=set(),\n            reason=f\"根据区间出号密度分析\"\n        )\n        self.results.append(result)\n    \n    def _kill_by_addsub(self):\n        \"\"\"加减法杀号 - 上期号码运算\"\"\"\n        if not self.latest:\n            return\n        \n        front = self.latest['front']\n        killed_front = set()\n        \n        # 方法1: 相邻号相减（大减小）\n        for i in range(len(front) - 1):\n            diff = front[i+1] - front[i]\n            if 1 <= diff <= 35:\n                killed_front.add(diff)\n        \n        # 方法2: 上期号码 +3，超过35则减35\n        for ball in front:\n            new_ball = ball + 3\n            if new_ball > 35:\n                new_ball -= 35\n            killed_front.add(new_ball)\n        \n        # 方法3: 上期号码 -3，小于1则加35\n        for ball in front:\n            new_ball = ball - 3\n            if new_ball < 1:\n                new_ball += 35\n            killed_front.add(new_ball)\n        \n        result = KillResult(\n            rule_name=\"加减法\",\n            killed_front=killed_front,\n            killed_back=set(),\n            reason=f\"基于上期号码: {' '.join(map(str, front))}\"\n        )\n        self.results.append(result)\n    \n    def _kill_by_formula(self):\n        \"\"\"公式杀号 - 三种经典公式\"\"\"\n        if not self.latest:\n            return\n        \n        front = sorted(self.latest['front'])\n        killed_front = set()\n        \n        # A1, A2, A3, A4, A5 分别为排序后的号码\n        A1, A2, A3, A4, A5 = front[0], front[1], front[2], front[3], front[4]\n        \n        # 公式1: A5 - A3 - A1 = B, 杀 B, B+1, B+3\n        B = A5 - A3 - A1\n        if B < 0:\n            B = abs(B)\n        for b in [B, B+1, B+3]:\n            if 1 <= b <= 35:\n                killed_front.add(b)\n        \n        # 公式2: A4 - A2 = C, 杀 C, C+10, C-10\n        C = A4 - A2\n        for c in [C, C+10, C-10]:\n            if 1 <= c <= 35:\n                killed_front.add(c)\n        \n        # 公式3: 杀 A5-A3, A3-A1, A5-A1\n        for diff in [A5-A3, A3-A1, A5-A1]:\n            if 1 <= diff <= 35:\n                killed_front.add(diff)\n        \n        result = KillResult(\n            rule_name=\"公式杀号\",\n            killed_front=killed_front,\n            killed_back=set(),\n            reason=f\"A5={A5}, A4={A4}, A3={A3}, A2={A2}, A1={A1}\"\n        )\n        self.results.append(result)\n    \n    def _kill_by_head_tail(self):\n        \"\"\"首尾联动杀号\"\"\"\n        if not self.latest:\n            return\n        \n        front = self.latest['front']\n        back = self.latest['back']\n        \n        # (最小前区 + 最大后区) % 35\n        min_front = min(front)\n        max_back = max(back)\n        \n        kill_ball = (min_front + max_back) % 35\n        if kill_ball == 0:\n            kill_ball = 35\n        \n        result = KillResult(\n            rule_name=\"首尾联动\",\n            killed_front={kill_ball},\n            killed_back=set(),\n            reason=f\"({min_front}+{max_back})%35={kill_ball}\"\n        )\n        self.results.append(result)\n    \n    def _kill_by_sum(self):\n        \"\"\"和值杀号 - 和值范围外杀号\"\"\"\n        if len(self.history) < 5:\n            return\n        \n        recent_sums = self.dm.get_recent_sums(self.history, 10)\n        if not recent_sums:\n            return\n        \n        avg_sum = sum(recent_sums) / len(recent_sums)\n        \n        # 前区和值范围大致在 60-120\n        # 如果上期和值偏离平均值太多，相邻和值范围的号码可能不会出\n        latest_sum = sum(self.latest['front'])\n        \n        killed_front = set()\n        \n        # 杀掉和值差异过大的号码组合（简化处理）\n        # 如果和值偏高，杀掉大号区的一些号码\n        if latest_sum > avg_sum + 10:\n            for ball in range(28, 36):\n                killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        result = KillResult(\n            rule_name=\"和值杀号\",\n            killed_front=killed_front,\n            killed_back=set(),\n            reason=f\"近期均值={avg_sum:.0f}, 上期={latest_sum}\"\n        )\n        self.results.append(result)\n    \n    def get_all_killed(self) -> Tuple[Set[int], Set[int]]:\n        \"\"\"获取所有被杀掉的号码\"\"\"\n        killed_front = set()\n        killed_back = set()\n        \n        for result in self.results:\n            killed_front |= result.killed_front\n            killed_back |= result.killed_back\n        \n        # 限制在有效范围内\n        killed_front = {b for b in killed_front if 1 <= b <= 35}\n        killed_back = {b for b in killed_back if 1 <= b <= 12}\n        \n        return killed_front, killed_back\n    \n    def get_high_confidence(self) -> Dict[int, List[str]]:\n        \"\"\"获取高置信度杀号（被多个规则同时命中）\"\"\"\n        # 统计每个号码被命中的次数\n        ball_hits = {}\n        \n        for result in self.results:\n            for ball in result.killed_front:\n                if ball not in ball_hits:\n                    ball_hits[ball] = []\n                ball_hits[ball].append(result.rule_name)\n        \n        # 筛选被2个及以上规则命中的号码\n        high_conf = {ball: rules for ball, rules in ball_hits.items() if len(rules) >= 2}\n        \n        return high_conf\n    \n    def get_remaining_pool(self) -> Tuple[List[int], List[int]]:\n        \"\"\"获取杀号后的剩余号码池\"\"\"\n        killed_front, killed_back = self.get_all_killed()\n        \n        remaining_front = [b for b in range(1, 36) if b not in killed_front]\n        remaining_back = [b for b in range(1, 13) if b not in killed_back]\n        \n        return remaining_front, remaining_back\n\n\ndef print_kill_results(results: List[KillResult], high_conf: dict):\n    \"\"\"打印杀号结果\"\"\"\n    print(\"\\n═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════\")\n    print(\"🔪 杀号详情\")\n    print(\"═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════\")\n    \n    for result in results:\n        if result.killed_front or result.killed_back:\n            front_str = ', '.join(map(str, sorted(result.killed_front))) if result.killed_front else '-'\n            back_str = ', '.join(map(str, sorted(result.killed_back))) if result.killed_back else '-'\n            \n            print(f\"\\n【{result.rule_name}】\")\n            if result.killed_front:\n                print(f\"  前区: {front_str}\")\n            if result.killed_back:\n                print(f\"  后区: {back_str}\")\n            if result.reason:\n                print(f\"  说明: {result.reason}\")\n    \n    # 高置信度\n    if high_conf:\n        print(\"\\n═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════\")\n        print(\"⭐ 高置信度杀号（≥2规则同时命中）\")\n        print(\"═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════\")\n        for ball, rules in sorted(high_conf.items()):\n            print(f\"  {ball:02d}号 ← {' + '.join(rules)}\")\n\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    # 测试\n    dm = DataManager()\n    history = dm.get_history(30)\n    stats = dm.get_statistics(history)\n    \n    engine = KillRuleEngine(history, stats)\n    results = engine.run_all()\n    \n    killed_front, killed_back = engine.get_all_killed()\n    remaining_front, remaining_back = engine.get_remaining_pool()\n    high_conf = engine.get_high_confidence()\n    \n    print(f\"前区杀号: {len(killed_front)}个\")\n    print(f\"后区杀号: {len(killed_back)}个\")\n    print(f\"前区剩余: {len(remaining_front)}个 - {remaining_front}\")\n    print(f\"后区剩余: {len(remaining_back)}个 - {remaining_back}\")\n    \n    print_kill_results(results, high_conf)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778413800612}}
{"type":"message","id":"f4828cfa","parentId":"eb3e9aa8","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:50:56.007Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要大幅优化杀号规则，核心改进：1. **保守冷热杀号**：\n   - 不杀热号（热号继续热的概率高）\n   - 只杀超冷号（遗漏超过数据量80%的号码）2. **遗漏杀号更保守**：\n   - 提高阈值（超过数据量90%）\n   - 排除上期刚出的号码（遗漏=0）3. **去掉加减法杀号**：\n   - 这个杀号太多且不准确\n   - 改为只在高置信度下使用4. **去掉公式杀号中的部分**：\n   - 公式2 (C+10, C-10) 太宽泛，容易误杀5. **只有高置信度（≥2规则）的才保留**：\n   - 单规则命中的号码要更严格的验证6. **增加过滤**：   - 排除遗漏=0的号码（上期刚出）\n   - 排除频率非常高的号码（热号继续热）","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yout56zy9jnm_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\n大乐透杀号选球技能 - 杀号规则引擎 v2\n优化版：提高杀号准确率，减少误杀\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom typing import List, Set, Dict, Tuple\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass, field\nfrom killer.data_manager import DataManager\n\n\n@dataclass\nclass KillResult:\n    \"\"\"杀号结果\"\"\"\n    rule_name: str\n    killed_front: Set[int] = field(default_factory=set)\n    killed_back: Set[int] = field(default_factory=set)\n    reason: str = \"\"\n    confidence: str = \"normal\"  # normal / high\n\n\nclass KillRuleEngine:\n    \"\"\"杀号规则引擎 v2\"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, history: List[dict], stats: dict = None):\n        self.history = history\n        self.latest = history[0] if history else None\n        self.stats = stats\n        self.results: List[KillResult] = []\n        self.dm = DataManager()\n    \n    def run_all(self) -> List[KillResult]:\n        \"\"\"执行所有杀号规则\"\"\"\n        if not self.stats:\n            self.stats = self.dm.get_statistics(self.history)\n        \n        self.results = []\n        \n        # 1. 保守遗漏杀号（只杀超冷号，排除上期刚出的）\n        self._kill_by_missing_conservative()\n        \n        # 2. 区间杀号（只杀长期断区）\n        self._kill_by_zone_conservative()\n        \n        # 3. 公式杀号（简化版，只用核心公式）\n        self._kill_by_formula_conservative()\n        \n        # 4. 首尾联动\n        self._kill_by_head_tail()\n        \n        # 5. 和值杀号（只在极端情况下）\n        self._kill_by_sum_conservative()\n        \n        return self.results\n    \n    def _kill_by_missing_conservative(self):\n        \"\"\"\n        保守遗漏杀号\n        改进：只杀超冷号，排除遗漏=0的号码\n        \"\"\"\n        front_missing = self.stats['front_missing']\n        back_missing = self.stats['back_missing']\n        front_count = self.stats['front_count']\n        back_count = self.stats['back_count']\n        total = self.stats['total']\n        \n        killed_front = set()\n        killed_back = set()\n        \n        # 前区：只杀遗漏超过90%分位且频率很低的号码\n        # 计算频率很低的标准：低于平均值的一半\n        front_avg = sum(front_count.values()) / 35\n        low_freq_threshold = front_avg * 0.5\n        \n        for ball in range(1, 36):\n            missing = front_missing[ball]\n            count = front_count[ball]\n            \n            # 条件：遗漏超过80%数据量 且 频率很低 且 不是上期刚出(遗漏>3)\n            if (missing >= total * 0.8 and \n                count < low_freq_threshold and \n                missing > 3):\n                killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        # 后区：遗漏超过80%且频率很低\n        back_avg = sum(back_count.values()) / 12\n        for ball in range(1, 13):\n            missing = back_missing[ball]\n            count = back_count[ball]\n            if missing >= total * 0.8 and count < back_avg * 0.5 and missing > 2:\n                killed_back.add(ball)\n        \n        result = KillResult(\n            rule_name=\"遗漏杀号\",\n            killed_front=killed_front,\n            killed_back=killed_back,\n            reason=f\"前区: 遗漏≥80%期数且频率低({len(killed_front)}个) | 后区: 同规则({len(killed_back)}个)\"\n        )\n        self.results.append(result)\n    \n    def _kill_by_zone_conservative(self):\n        \"\"\"\n        保守区间杀号\n        改进：只杀完全没出号的区，且该区总出号数极少\n        \"\"\"\n        zones = self.stats['zones']\n        total = self.stats['total']\n        \n        killed_front = set()\n        \n        # 7区划分\n        for zone_id in range(1, 8):\n            balls_in_zone = zones.get(zone_id, [])\n            \n            # 该区出号密度 = 该区出现次数 / 总期数\n            density = len(balls_in_zone) / total if total > 0 else 0\n            \n            # 条件：该区出号密度 < 3% 且 上期该区没有号码\n            if density < 0.03:\n                # 检查上期该区是否有号码\n                zone_start = (zone_id - 1) * 5 + 1\n                zone_end = zone_id * 5 + 1\n                has_recent = any(zone_start <= b < zone_end for b in self.latest['front'])\n                \n                if not has_recent:\n                    # 杀掉该区号码\n                    for ball in range(zone_start, min(zone_end, 36)):\n                        killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        result = KillResult(\n            rule_name=\"断区杀号\",\n            killed_front=killed_front,\n            killed_back=set(),\n            reason=f\"出号密度<3%且上期无出号\"\n        )\n        self.results.append(result)\n    \n    def _kill_by_formula_conservative(self):\n        \"\"\"\n        简化公式杀号\n        改进：只用核心公式，减少误杀\n        \"\"\"\n        if not self.latest:\n            return\n        \n        front = sorted(self.latest['front'])\n        killed_front = set()\n        front_missing = self.stats['front_missing']\n        front_count = self.stats['front_count']\n        total = self.stats['total']\n        \n        A1, A2, A3, A4, A5 = front[0], front[1], front[2], front[3], front[4]\n        \n        # 只用公式1：核心公式 (A5 - A3 - A1)\n        B = A5 - A3 - A1\n        if B < 0:\n            B = abs(B)\n        \n        # 只杀 B 和 B+1，不杀 B+3\n        for b in [B, B+1]:\n            if 1 <= b <= 35:\n                # 进一步验证：该号码当前遗漏较高或频率很低\n                if front_missing[b] > total * 0.3 or front_count[b] < 3:\n                    killed_front.add(b)\n        \n        # 公式3简化：只取最大的差值\n        diff1 = A5 - A1\n        diff2 = A3 - A1\n        diff3 = A5 - A3\n        \n        for diff in [diff1, diff2, diff3]:\n            if 1 <= diff <= 35:\n                if front_missing[diff] > total * 0.4 or front_count[diff] < 3:\n                    killed_front.add(diff)\n        \n        result = KillResult(\n            rule_name=\"公式杀号\",\n            killed_front=killed_front,\n            killed_back=set(),\n            reason=f\"简化公式1+3，且验证遗漏/频率\"\n        )\n        self.results.append(result)\n    \n    def _kill_by_head_tail(self):\n        \"\"\"首尾联动杀号\"\"\"\n        if not self.latest:\n            return\n        \n        front = self.latest['front']\n        back = self.latest['back']\n        front_missing = self.stats['front_missing']\n        total = self.stats['total']\n        \n        min_front = min(front)\n        max_back = max(back)\n        \n        kill_ball = (min_front + max_back) % 35\n        if kill_ball == 0:\n            kill_ball = 35\n        \n        # 只有当该号码遗漏较高时才杀\n        if front_missing[kill_ball] > total * 0.3:\n            result = KillResult(\n                rule_name=\"首尾联动\",\n                killed_front={kill_ball},\n                killed_back=set(),\n                reason=f\"({min_front}+{max_back})%35={kill_ball}，遗漏={front_missing[kill_ball]}\"\n            )\n        else:\n            result = KillResult(\n                rule_name=\"首尾联动\",\n                killed_front=set(),\n                killed_back=set(),\n                reason=f\"({min_front}+{max_back})%35={kill_ball}，遗漏不足，跳过\"\n            )\n        \n        self.results.append(result)\n    \n    def _kill_by_sum_conservative(self):\n        \"\"\"\n        保守和值杀号\n        改进：只在极端情况下才杀\n        \"\"\"\n        if len(self.history) < 5:\n            return\n        \n        recent_sums = self.dm.get_recent_sums(self.history, 10)\n        if not recent_sums:\n            return\n        \n        avg_sum = sum(recent_sums) / len(recent_sums)\n        latest_sum = sum(self.latest['front'])\n        \n        killed_front = set()\n        \n        # 只有当上期和值偏离平均值超过25%（极端情况）才杀\n        if abs(latest_sum - avg_sum) / avg_sum > 0.25:\n            # 和值偏高，杀大号区\n            if latest_sum > avg_sum * 1.25:\n                for ball in range(30, 36):\n                    killed_front.add(ball)\n            # 和值偏低，杀小号区\n            elif latest_sum < avg_sum * 0.75:\n                for ball in range(1, 8):\n                    killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        result = KillResult(\n            rule_name=\"和值杀号\",\n            killed_front=killed_front,\n            killed_back=set(),\n            reason=f\"偏离均值>25%时触发，当前偏离{abs(latest_sum-avg_sum)/avg_sum*100:.0f}%\"\n        )\n        self.results.append(result)\n    \n    def get_all_killed(self) -> Tuple[Set[int], Set[int]]:\n        \"\"\"获取所有被杀掉的号码\"\"\"\n        killed_front = set()\n        killed_back = set()\n        \n        for result in self.results:\n            killed_front |= result.killed_front\n            killed_back |= result.killed_back\n        \n        # 限制在有效范围内\n        killed_front = {b for b in killed_front if 1 <= b <= 35}\n        killed_back = {b for b in killed_back if 1 <= b <= 12}\n        \n        return killed_front, killed_back\n    \n    def get_high_confidence(self) -> Dict[int, List[str]]:\n        \"\"\"获取高置信度杀号（被多个规则同时命中）\"\"\"\n        ball_hits = {}\n        \n        for result in self.results:\n            for ball in result.killed_front:\n                if ball not in ball_hits:\n                    ball_hits[ball] = []\n                ball_hits[ball].append(result.rule_name)\n        \n        # 筛选被2个及以上规则命中的号码\n        high_conf = {ball: rules for ball, rules in ball_hits.items() if len(rules) >= 2}\n        \n        return high_conf\n    \n    def get_remaining_pool(self) -> Tuple[List[int], List[int]]:\n        \"\"\"获取杀号后的剩余号码池\"\"\"\n        killed_front, killed_back = self.get_all_killed()\n        \n        remaining_front = [b for b in range(1, 36) if b not in killed_front]\n        remaining_back = [b for b in range(1, 13) if b not in killed_back]\n        \n        return remaining_front, remaining_back\n\n\ndef print_kill_results(results: List[KillResult], high_conf: dict):\n    \"\"\"打印杀号结果\"\"\"\n    print(\"\\n═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════\")\n    print(\"🔪 杀号详情\")\n    print(\"═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════\")\n    \n    for result in results:\n        if result.killed_front or result.killed_back:\n            front_str = ', '.join(f\"{b:02d}\" for b in sorted(result.killed_front)) if result.killed_front else '-'\n            back_str = ', '.join(f\"{b:02d}\" for b in sorted(result.killed_back)) if result.killed_back else '-'\n            \n            print(f\"\\n【{result.rule_name}】\")\n            if result.killed_front:\n                print(f\"  前区: {front_str}\")\n            if result.killed_back:\n                print(f\"  后区: {back_str}\")\n            if result.reason:\n                print(f\"  说明: {result.reason}\")\n    \n    if high_conf:\n        print(\"\\n═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════\")\n        print(\"⭐ 高置信度杀号（≥2规则同时命中）\")\n        print(\"═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════\")\n        for ball, rules in sorted(high_conf.items()):\n            print(f\"  {ball:02d}号 ← {' + '.join(rules)}\")\n\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    dm = DataManager()\n    history = dm.get_history(30)\n    stats = dm.get_statistics(history)\n    \n    engine = KillRuleEngine(history, stats)\n    results = engine.run_all()\n    \n    killed_front, killed_back = engine.get_all_killed()\n    remaining_front, remaining_back = engine.get_remaining_pool()\n    high_conf = engine.get_high_confidence()\n    \n    print(f\"前区杀号: {len(killed_front)}个\")\n    print(f\"后区杀号: {len(killed_back)}个\")\n    print(f\"前区剩余: {len(remaining_front)}个\")\n    print(f\"后区剩余: {len(remaining_back)}个\")\n    \n    print_kill_results(results, high_conf)\n","path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/kill_rules.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":5242,"output":3356,"cacheRead":99899,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108497,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778413800614,"responseId":"064fa3e943e159318fbdbae57d5dceb0"}}
