":0,"durationMs":48,"aggregated":"被杀号码命中详情：\n==================================================\n期: 杀[5, 10, 14, 23, 31]... 实际[9, 20, 21, 23, 28] 命中1个\n期: 杀[1, 4, 5, 10, 15, 23, 31]... 实际[1, 15, 21, 26, 33] 命中2个\n期: 杀[1, 10, 14, 15, 23, 31]... 实际[8, 12, 14, 19, 22] 命中1个\n期: 杀[1, 10, 14, 15, 16, 23, 24, 31]... 实际[24, 25, 27, 29, 34] 命中1个\n期: 杀[1, 6, 10, 13, 14, 15, 20, 23, 24, 31]... 实际[9, 11, 20, 26, 27] 命中1个\n期: 杀[1, 6, 10, 13, 14, 15, 19, 20, 21, 23]... 实际[8, 17, 21, 33, 35] 命中1个\n期: 杀[1, 10, 13, 14, 15, 16, 20, 21, 23, 24]... 实际[7, 12, 13, 28, 32] 命中1个\n期: 杀[1, 4, 10, 14, 16, 20, 21, 23, 24, 30]... 实际[4, 7, 16, 26, 32] 命中3个\n期: 杀[1, 2, 10, 14, 16, 20, 21, 23, 24, 31]... 实际[2, 22, 30, 33, 34] 命中1个\n期: 杀[1, 4, 11, 14, 15, 20, 21, 23, 24, 25]... 实际[11, 12, 25, 26, 27] 命中2个\n期: 杀[1, 7, 10, 11, 13, 14, 15, 16, 18, 20]... 实际[3, 5, 7, 9, 18] 命中2个\n期: 杀[1, 4, 6, 7, 12, 14, 16, 18, 19, 20]... 实际[3, 4, 19, 26, 32] 命中2个\n期: 杀[1, 4, 6, 7, 8, 11, 12, 14, 18, 19]... 实际[6, 8, 22, 29, 34] 命中2个\n期: 杀[1, 2, 4, 6, 7, 8, 13, 14, 15, 16]... 实际[2, 13, 22, 28, 34] 命中2个\n期: 杀[1, 2, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 11, 13, 14]... 实际[3, 5, 17, 33, 35] 命中4个\n期: 杀[1, 2, 4, 5, 6, 7, 13, 14, 17, 18]... 实际[15, 27, 29, 30, 34] 命中3个\n期: 杀[1, 5, 6, 7, 9, 12, 13, 14, 16, 17]... 实际[9, 10, 11, 12, 16] 命中3个\n期: 杀[1, 2, 3, 5, 6, 7, 11, 12, 13, 14]... 实际[10, 11, 22, 26, 32] 命中4个\n期: 杀[1, 3, 6, 7, 11, 12, 13, 14, 15, 16]... 实际[3, 15, 24, 28, 29] 命中4个\n期: 杀[1, 2, 3, 4, 6, 7, 8, 11, 13, 15]... 实际[2, 4, 8, 10, 21] 命中4个\n期: 杀[5, 11, 12, 16, 21, 22, 23, 24, 25, 31]... 实际[9, 25, 26, 27, 28] 命中1个\n\n==================================================\n被命中次数最多的号码：\n  04号: 被杀中3次\n  02号: 被杀中3次\n  15号: 被杀中2次\n  24号: 被杀中2次\n  21号: 被杀中2次\n  13号: 被杀中2次\n  32号: 被杀中2次\n  16号: 被杀中2次\n  11号: 被杀中2次\n  25号: 被杀中2次","cwd":"/workspace/projects/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778413983513}}
{"type":"message","id":"e9079e10","parentId":"b96c53d3","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:53:23.934Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到问题了！被杀中的号码主要是：- 04, 02号被杀了多次- 遗漏杀号杀了04、02等高频号码（遗漏值在50%左右但实际是高频号）\n- 断区杀号也杀了很多不该杀的号\n\n问题分析：\n1. **遗漏50%阈值太宽**：04号遗漏14期（14/30=46.7%），02号遗漏8期（8/30=26.7%），但它们出现频率并不低\n2. **断区杀号误杀**：把很多区的高频号码也杀掉了3. **公式杀号误杀**：把差值运算出的号码杀掉，但这些号码可能频率不低\n\n解决方案：\n1. **提高遗漏阈值**：从50%提高到70%\n2. **排除高频号码**：如果一个号码出现频率很高，即使遗漏高也不杀\n3. **更严格的断区条件**：只有长期断区才杀\n4. **增加验证**：被杀号必须同时满足多个条件","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"发现问题！04、02号被误杀多次。需要提高阈值并增加条件验证：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9ohxu2353t5b_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    def _kill_by_missing_conservative(self):\n        \"\"\"\n        保守遗漏杀号\n        改进：遗漏超过70%期数 且 频率低于平均值\n        排除高频号码和上期刚出的号码\n        \"\"\"\n        front_missing = self.stats['front_missing']\n        back_missing = self.stats['back_missing']\n        front_count = self.stats['front_count']\n        back_count = self.stats['back_count']\n        total = self.stats['total']\n        \n        killed_front = set()\n        killed_back = set()\n        \n        # 前区平均频率\n        front_avg = sum(front_count.values()) / 35\n        \n        for ball in range(1, 36):\n            missing = front_missing[ball]\n            count = front_count[ball]\n            \n            # 严格条件：\n            # 1. 遗漏超过70%期数\n            # 2. 频率低于平均值（不是高频号）\n            # 3. 排除上期刚出的号码（遗漏>3）\n            # 4. 排除从不出号但可能是冷号的（出现至少1次）\n            if (missing >= total * 0.7 and \n                missing > 3 and\n                count < front_avg and\n                count >= 1):\n                killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        # 后区平均频率\n        back_avg = sum(back_count.values()) / 12\n        for ball in range(1, 13):\n            missing = back_missing[ball]\n            count = back_count[ball]\n            if (missing >= total * 0.7 and \n                missing > 3 and\n                count < back_avg and\n                count >= 1):\n                killed_back.add(ball)\n        \n        result = KillResult(\n            rule_name=\"遗漏杀号\",\n            killed_front=killed_front,\n            killed_back=killed_back,\n            reason=f\"前区: 遗漏≥70%期数且频率<均值({len(killed_front)}个) | 后区: 同规则({len(killed_back)}个)\"\n        )\n        self.results.append(result)","oldText":"    def _kill_by_missing_conservative(self):\n        \"\"\"\n        保守遗漏杀号\n        改进：遗漏超过50%期数且频率低于平均的号码，排除上期刚出的\n        \"\"\"\n        front_missing = self.stats['front_missing']\n        back_missing = self.stats['back_missing']\n        front_count = self.stats['front_count']\n        back_count = self.stats['back_count']\n        total = self.stats['total']\n        \n        killed_front = set()\n        killed_back = set()\n        \n        # 前区：遗漏超过50%期数 且 频率低于平均值\n        front_avg = sum(front_count.values()) / 35\n        \n        for ball in range(1, 36):\n            missing = front_missing[ball]\n            count = front_count[ball]\n            \n            # 条件：遗漏超过50%期数 且 不是上期刚出(遗漏>2)\n            if missing >= total * 0.5 and missing > 2:\n                killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        # 后区：遗漏超过50%期数\n        for ball in range(1, 13):\n            missing = back_missing[ball]\n            if missing >= total * 0.5 and missing > 2:\n                killed_back.add(ball)\n        \n        result = KillResult(\n            rule_name=\"遗漏杀号\",\n            killed_front=killed_front,\n            killed_back=killed_back,\n            reason=f\"前区: 遗漏≥50%期数({len(killed_front)}个) | 后区: 同规则({len(killed_back)}个)\"\n        )\n        self.results.append(result)"}],"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/kill_rules.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":15555,"output":1407,"cacheRead":104827,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121789,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778413983516,"responseId":"064fa49f7704cfc7f534dd0127b1ea0f"}}
