{"type":"message","id":"aa7da580","parentId":"70de2ca9","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:54:00.506Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"效果改善：\n- 前区命中率从1.73降低到0.77\n- 前区完全没漏从19.2%提升到50%\n\n但准确率从88.3%降到84.9%，而杀号数量从13.4降到6.3。\n\n问题：现在的杀号策略过于保守，只杀了1个号码。让我分析一下为什么31号没被杀：31号：出现0次，遗漏30期\n- 遗漏 >= 30 * 0.7 = 21 ✓\n- 遗漏 > 3 ✓- 频率 < 均值 ✓\n- 频率 >= 1 ✗ (31号从未出现)所以31号被排除了，因为它从未出现（count=0）。\n\n这是一个权衡问题：\n1. 遗漏极高但从未出现的号码，可能突然出现\n2. 所以我们设置了 count >= 1 的条件但这样导致31号没被杀。让我调整策略：\n1. 如果遗漏超过90%，即使从未出现也要杀2. 或者增加更多的杀号规则","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n命中降低了（0.77），但杀的太少（只杀1个）。需要增加一些有效杀号。让我分析31号为什么没被杀：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gnbflz8va8mg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer && python -c '\nfrom killer.data_manager import DataManager\ndm = DataManager()\nhistory = dm.get_history(30)\nstats = dm.get_statistics(history)\n\nprint(\"31号分析:\")\nprint(f\"  出现次数: {stats[\\\"front_count\\\"][31]}\")\nprint(f\"  当前遗漏: {stats[\\\"front_missing\\\"][31]}\")\nprint(f\"  总期数: {stats[\\\"total\\\"]}\")\nprint(f\"  遗漏占比: {stats[\\\"front_missing\\\"][31]/stats[\\\"total\\\"]*100:.1f}%\")\n'","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":1172,"output":630,"cacheRead":123195,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124997,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778414030632,"responseId":"064fa4cf29c55450590514e36d3e9779"}}
