{"type":"message","id":"6150a092","parentId":"8151d668","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:54:21.190Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"31号从未出现（count=0），所以被我的条件 count >= 1 排除了。但它遗漏了100%的期数，这是极端情况。让我增加一个特殊规则：对于遗漏100%或从未出现的号码，也需要谨慎对待，但可以给一个单独的判断。\n\n但更好的策略是：增加一些辅助杀号规则来增加杀号数量，同时保持高准确率。\n\n让我重新设计策略：1. **增加一个\"超冷号杀号\"**：遗漏>=90%的号码，无论频率\n2. **增加\"连续未出现杀号\"**：从未出现的号码（如果总数据量够大）","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"31号从未出现被排除了。让我增加一个\"超冷号\"规则：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dz3frmqhws46_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    def run_all(self) -> List[KillResult]:\n        \"\"\"执行所有杀号规则\"\"\"\n        if not self.stats:\n            self.stats = self.dm.get_statistics(self.history)\n        \n        self.results = []\n        \n        # 1. 超冷号杀号（从未出现或遗漏>90%期数）\n        self._kill_by_extreme_cold()\n        \n        # 2. 保守遗漏杀号（遗漏超过70%期数且频率低于平均）\n        self._kill_by_missing_conservative()\n        \n        # 3. 区间杀号（只杀长期断区）\n        self._kill_by_zone_conservative()\n        \n        # 4. 公式杀号（简化版）\n        self._kill_by_formula_conservative()\n        \n        # 5. 首尾联动\n        self._kill_by_head_tail()\n        \n        # 6. 和值杀号（只在极端情况下）\n        self._kill_by_sum_conservative()\n        \n        return self.results\n    \n    def _kill_by_extreme_cold(self):\n        \"\"\"\n        超冷号杀号\n        从未出现的号码（遗漏100%）可能本期也不出\n        \"\"\"\n        front_missing = self.stats['front_missing']\n        back_missing = self.stats['back_missing']\n        front_count = self.stats['front_count']\n        back_count = self.stats['back_count']\n        total = self.stats['total']\n        \n        killed_front = set()\n        killed_back = set()\n        \n        # 前区：从未出现（遗漏100%）且数据量足够（至少20期）\n        if total >= 20:\n            for ball in range(1, 36):\n                if front_count[ball] == 0:\n                    killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        # 后区：从未出现\n        for ball in range(1, 13):\n            if back_count[ball] == 0:\n                killed_back.add(ball)\n        \n        if killed_front or killed_back:\n            result = KillResult(\n                rule_name=\"超冷杀号\",\n                killed_front=killed_front,\n                killed_back=killed_back,\n                reason=f\"前区从未出现({len(killed_front)}个) | 后区从未出现({len(killed_back)}个)\"\n            )\n            self.results.append(result)","oldText":"    def run_all(self) -> List[KillResult]:\n        \"\"\"执行所有杀号规则\"\"\"\n        if not self.stats:\n            self.stats = self.dm.get_statistics(self.history)\n        \n        self.results = []\n        \n        # 1. 保守遗漏杀号（只杀超冷号，排除上期刚出的）\n        self._kill_by_missing_conservative()\n        \n        # 2. 区间杀号（只杀长期断区）\n        self._kill_by_zone_conservative()\n        \n        # 3. 公式杀号（简化版）\n        self._kill_by_formula_conservative()\n        \n        # 4. 首尾联动\n        self._kill_by_head_tail()\n        \n        # 5. 和值杀号（只在极端情况下）\n        self._kill_by_sum_conservative()\n        \n        return self.results"}],"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/kill_rules.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":65,"output":1133,"cacheRead":124987,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126185,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778414045161,"responseId":"064fa4dd574283953723324a7dab7aef"}}
