{"type":"message","id":"00e916cd","parentId":"251ee27a","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:55:45.096Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"效果改善明显！\n- **前区命中率**：从0.77进一步降低到**0.38**（平均每期只杀中0.38个开奖号码）\n- **前区完全没漏**：从50%提升到**61.5%**（超过60%的期次完全没漏）- **平均杀号数量**：3.8个（从6.3降到3.8，更保守）- **准确率**：89.7%（接近90%）但准确率还没到95%。让我分析一下回测中那些被杀中的号码是什么情况。问题：准确率89.7%意味着杀的号码中有10.3%是实际开奖号码。平均杀3.8个，意味着平均0.38个是实际号码，这已经是很好的结果了。\n\n要达到95%准确率，意味着杀的3.8个号码中最多只有0.19个是实际号码（3.8 * 0.05 = 0.19）。\n\n现在的情况：\n- 杀的号码数：3.8个- 命中数：0.38个\n- 准确率：89.7%\n\n准确率 = (3.8 - 0.38) / 3.8 = 90%\n\n如果想达到95%准确率：\n- 杀的号码数：x\n- 命中数：x * 0.05\n- 准确率：(x - x*0.05) / x = 95%\n\n\n需要在保持命中率稳定的前提下扩大杀号规模，或者通过多规则组合验证来提升准确率。不过0.38的命中率已经是相当保守的结果，30期数据可能还不足以进一步优化。我应该考虑是否加入更多有效的杀号规则。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"效果显著改善！\n\n## 📊 优化结果对比\n\n| 指标 | 优化前 | 优化后 |\n|------|--------|--------|\n| 平均杀号数 | 13.4个 | **3.8个** |\n| 命中率 | 1.73个/期 | **0.38个/期** |\n| 完全没漏 | 19.2% | **61.5%** |\n| 准确率 | 88.3% | **89.7%** |\n\n命中降到0.38，已非常保守！但准确率89.7%离95%还有差距。\n\n让我查看详细命中分析，找出可优化的空间：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u2o1xc9qv1ua_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer && python -c \"\nfrom killer.data_manager import DataManager\nfrom killer.backtest import BacktestEngine\n\ndm = DataManager()\nhistory = dm.get_history(30)\n\nbt = BacktestEngine(history)\nresult = bt.run_backtest(skip_recent=3)\n\nprint('命中详情分析：')\nprint('=' * 50)\n\nmissed = []  # 杀的号码中命中的详情\nfor r in result['details']:\n    killed = r['killed_front']\n    actual = set(r['actual_front'])\n    hit = killed & actual\n    if hit:\n        print(f'期: 杀{sorted(killed)} 实际{sorted(actual)} 命中{sorted(hit)}')\n\nprint()\nprint('被命中号码统计：')\nfrom collections import Counter\nhit_balls = []\nfor r in result['details']:\n    hit_balls.extend(list(r['killed_front'] & set(r['actual_front'])))\nc = Counter(hit_balls)\nfor ball, cnt in c.most_common():\n    print(f'  {ball}号: 被杀中{cnt}次')\n\"","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":12933,"output":1114,"cacheRead":120059,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134106,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778414126241,"responseId":"064fa52e582827813f82d47ea943cf02"}}
