{"type":"message","id":"68c6c9a5","parentId":"2b9af27b","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:55:57.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到问题了！1. **31号**：在第1期被杀中（因为从未出现被杀掉，但实际开了31）\n2. **23号**：被超冷杀号杀掉（从未出现），但实际开了\n3. **1号、14号、24号、21号、18号、17号、32号、25号**：这些是公式杀号的结果问题分析：\n- 超冷杀号杀掉了从未出现的号码，但这些号码有时会突然出现（概率虽低但不是0）\n- 公式杀号仍然有一定误杀率解决方案：\n1. **降低超冷杀号的权重**：从不出现的号码中只选一部分杀掉\n2. **增加更多验证条件**：被杀的号码需要满足多个条件\n3. **只保留高置信度杀号**：单规则命中的号码要更严格","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"发现超冷杀号和公式杀号有较多误杀。让我调整策略，只保留高置信度杀号：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_x167l13fo9zb_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    def run_all(self) -> List[KillResult]:\n        \"\"\"执行所有杀号规则（只保留高置信度）\"\"\"\n        if not self.stats:\n            self.stats = self.dm.get_statistics(self.history)\n        \n        self.results = []\n        \n        # 只保留最保守的杀号规则\n        \n        # 1. 超冷号杀号（从未出现，数据量≥25期才启用）\n        self._kill_by_extreme_cold()\n        \n        # 2. 区间杀号（超严格条件）\n        self._kill_by_zone_strict()\n        \n        return self.results","oldText":"    def run_all(self) -> List[KillResult]:\n        \"\"\"执行所有杀号规则\"\"\"\n        if not self.stats:\n            self.stats = self.dm.get_statistics(self.history)\n        \n        self.results = []\n        \n        # 1. 超冷号杀号（从未出现）\n        self._kill_by_extreme_cold()\n        \n        # 2. 保守遗漏杀号（遗漏>70%且频率低）\n        self._kill_by_missing_conservative()\n        \n        # 3. 区间杀号\n        self._kill_by_zone_conservative()\n        \n        # 4. 公式杀号\n        self._kill_by_formula_conservative()\n        \n        # 5. 首尾联动\n        self._kill_by_head_tail()\n        \n        return self.results"}],"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/kill_rules.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":782,"output":798,"cacheRead":133499,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135079,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778414145153,"responseId":"064fa541920cb80d2dcd2092454ae0d3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ebc2c354","parentId":"68c6c9a5","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:55:57.018Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_x167l13fo9zb_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/kill_rules.py."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n  28         self.results: List[KillResult] = []\n  29         self.dm = DataManager()\n  30     \n  31     def run_all(self) -> List[KillResult]:\n- 32         \"\"\"执行所有杀号规则\"\"\"\n+ 32         \"\"\"执行所有杀号规则（只保留高置信度）\"\"\"\n  33         if not self.stats:\n  34             self.stats = self.dm.get_statistics(self.history)\n  35         \n  36         self.results = []\n  37         \n- 38         # 1. 超冷号杀号（从未出现）\n+ 38         # 只保留最保守的杀号规则\n+ 39         \n+ 40         # 1. 超冷号杀号（从未出现，数据量≥25期才启用）\n  39         self._kill_by_extreme_cold()\n  40         \n- 41         # 2. 保守遗漏杀号（遗漏>70%且频率低）\n- 42         self._kill_by_missing_conservative()\n+ 43         # 2. 区间杀号（超严格条件）\n+ 44         self._kill_by_zone_strict()\n  43         \n- 44         # 3. 区间杀号\n- 45         self._kill_by_zone_conservative()\n- 46         \n- 47         # 4. 公式杀号\n- 48         self._kill_by_formula_conservative()\n- 49         \n- 50         # 5. 首尾联动\n- 51         self._kill_by_head_tail()\n- 52         \n  53         return self.results\n  54     \n  55     def _kill_by_extreme_cold(self):\n  56         \"\"\"超冷号杀号：从未出现的号码\"\"\"\n     ...","firstChangedLine":32},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778414157018}}
{"type":"message","id":"ba1c2ac0","parentId":"ebc2c354","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:56:22.054Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要增加一个更严格的区间杀号规则，替换掉原来的_conservative版本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_m797x9jv3e3q_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    def _kill_by_extreme_cold(self):\n        \"\"\"超冷号杀号：从未出现的号码（数据量≥25期才启用）\"\"\"\n        front_count = self.stats['front_count']\n        back_count = self.stats['back_count']\n        total = self.stats['total']\n        \n        killed_front = set()\n        killed_back = set()\n        \n        # 前区：从未来过且数据量足够\n        if total >= 25:\n            for ball in range(1, 36):\n                if front_count[ball] == 0:\n                    killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        # 后区：从未出现\n        if total >= 25:\n            for ball in range(1, 13):\n                if back_count[ball] == 0:\n                    killed_back.add(ball)\n        \n        if killed_front or killed_back:\n            result = KillResult(\n                rule_name=\"超冷杀号\",\n                killed_front=killed_front,\n                killed_back=killed_back,\n                reason=f\"从未出现({len(killed_front)}个)\"\n            )\n            self.results.append(result)\n    \n    def _kill_by_zone_strict(self):\n        \"\"\"严格区间杀号：只杀超低密度区间\"\"\"\n        zones = self.stats['zones']\n        total = self.stats['total']\n        front_count = self.stats['front_count']\n        front_avg = sum(front_count.values()) / 35\n        \n        killed_front = set()\n        \n        for zone_id in range(1, 8):\n            balls_in_zone = zones.get(zone_id, [])\n            density = len(balls_in_zone) / total if total > 0 else 0\n            \n            # 超严格：密度<3% 且 上期无出号 且 全部为低频\n            if density < 0.03:\n                zone_start = (zone_id - 1) * 5 + 1\n                zone_end = zone_id * 5 + 1\n                has_recent = any(zone_start <= b < zone_end for b in self.latest['front'])\n                \n                if not has_recent:\n                    all_low_freq = all(front_count[b] < front_avg * 0.5 for b in range(zone_start, min(zone_end, 36)))\n                    if all_low_freq:\n                        for ball in range(zone_start, min(zone_end, 36)):\n                            killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        if killed_front:\n            result = KillResult(\n                rule_name=\"断区杀号\",\n                killed_front=killed_front,\n                killed_back=set(),\n                reason=f\"密度<3%且全部低频\"\n            )\n            self.results.append(result)","oldText":"    def _kill_by_extreme_cold(self):\n        \"\"\"超冷号杀号：从未出现的号码\"\"\"\n        front_count = self.stats['front_count']\n        back_count = self.stats['back_count']\n        total = self.stats['total']\n        \n        killed_front = set()\n        killed_back = set()\n        \n        # 前区：从未来过（遗漏100%）\n        if total >= 20:\n            for ball in range(1, 36):\n                if front_count[ball] == 0:\n                    killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        # 后区：从未出现\n        for ball in range(1, 13):\n            if back_count[ball] == 0:\n                killed_back.add(ball)\n        \n        if killed_front or killed_back:\n            result = KillResult(\n                rule_name=\"超冷杀号\",\n                killed_front=killed_front,\n                killed_back=killed_back,\n                reason=f\"前区从未出现({len(killed_front)}个) | 后区从未出现({len(killed_back)}个)\"\n            )\n            self.results.append(result)\n    \n    def _kill_by_missing_conservative(self):\n        \"\"\"保守遗漏杀号\"\"\"\n        front_missing = self.stats['front_missing']\n        back_missing = self.stats['back_missing']\n        front_count = self.stats['front_count']\n        back_count = self.stats['back_count']\n        total = self.stats['total']\n        \n        killed_front = set()\n        killed_back = set()\n        \n        front_avg = sum(front_count.values()) / 35\n        \n        for ball in range(1, 36):\n            missing = front_missing[ball]\n            count = front_count[ball]\n            \n            # 遗漏>70% 且 频率<均值 且 出现≥1次 且 遗漏>3\n            if (missing >= total * 0.7 and \n                missing > 3 and\n                count < front_avg and\n                count >= 1):\n                killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        back_avg = sum(back_count.values()) / 12\n        for ball in range(1, 13):\n            missing = back_missing[ball]\n            count = back_count[ball]\n            if (missing >= total * 0.7 and \n                missing > 3 and\n                count < back_avg and\n                count >= 1):\n                killed_back.add(ball)\n        \n        if killed_front or killed_back:\n            result = KillResult(\n                rule_name=\"遗漏杀号\",\n                killed_front=killed_front,\n                killed_back=killed_back,\n                reason=f\"遗漏≥70%期数且频率<均值({len(killed_front)}个)\"\n            )\n            self.results.append(result)\n    \n    def _kill_by_zone_conservative(self):\n        \"\"\"区间杀号\"\"\"\n        zones = self.stats['zones']\n        total = self.stats['total']\n        front_count = self.stats['front_count']\n        front_avg = sum(front_count.values()) / 35\n        \n        killed_front = set()\n        \n        for zone_id in range(1, 8):\n            balls_in_zone = zones.get(zone_id, [])\n            density = len(balls_in_zone) / total if total > 0 else 0\n            \n            # 密度<5% 且 上期无出号 且 全部低频\n            if density < 0.05:\n                zone_start = (zone_id - 1) * 5 + 1\n                zone_end = zone_id * 5 + 1\n                has_recent = any(zone_start <= b < zone_end for b in self.latest['front'])\n                \n                if not has_recent:\n                    all_low_freq = all(front_count[b] < front_avg for b in range(zone_start, min(zone_end, 36)))\n                    if all_low_freq:\n                        for ball in range(zone_start, min(zone_end, 36)):\n                            killed_front.add(ball)\n        \n        if killed_front:\n            result = KillResult(\n                rule_name=\"断区杀号\",\n                killed_front=killed_front,\n                killed_back=set(),\n                reason=f\"密度<5%且上期无出号\"\n            )\n            self.results.append(result)\n    \n    def _kill_by_formula_conservative(self):\n        \"\"\"公式杀号\"\"\"\n        if not self.latest:\n            return\n        \n        front = sorted(self.latest['front'])\n        killed_front = set()\n        front_missing = self.stats['front_missing']\n        front_count = self.stats['front_count']\n        total = self.stats['total']\n        \n        A1, A2, A3, A4, A5 = front[0], front[1], front[2], front[3], front[4]\n        \n        # 公式1：(A5-A3-A1)\n        B = A5 - A3 - A1\n        if B < 0:\n            B = abs(B)\n        if B > 0:\n            killed_front.add(B)\n        \n        # 公式2：(A5-A1)\n        diff1 = A5 - A1\n        if 1 <= diff1 <= 35:\n            killed_front.add(diff1)\n        \n        # 验证：只有遗漏较高的才杀\n        final_killed = set()\n        for ball in killed_front:\n            if front_missing[ball] > total * 0.4:\n                final_killed.add(ball)\n        \n        if final_killed:\n            result = KillResult(\n                rule_name=\"公式杀号\",\n                killed_front=final_killed,\n                killed_back=set(),\n                reason=f\"差值公式，遗漏>40%\"\n            )\n            self.results.append(result)\n    \n    def _kill_by_head_tail(self):\n        \"\"\"首尾联动\"\"\"\n        if not self.latest:\n            return\n        \n        front = self.latest['front']\n        back = self.latest['back']\n        front_missing = self.stats['front_missing']\n        total = self.stats['total']\n        \n        min_front = min(front)\n        max_back = max(back)\n        \n        kill_ball = (min_front + max_back) % 35\n        if kill_ball == 0:\n            kill_ball = 35\n        \n        # 遗漏>50%才杀\n        if front_missing[kill_ball] > total * 0.5:\n            result = KillResult(\n                rule_name=\"首尾联动\",\n                killed_front={kill_ball},\n                killed_back=set(),\n                reason=f\"({min_front}+{max_back})%35={kill_ball}，遗漏>{total*0.5}\"\n            )\n            self.results.append(result)"}],"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto-killer/killer/kill_rules.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":101,"output":2403,"cacheRead":134843,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137347,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778414157022,"responseId":"064fa54d52f8a27127fd800d30750bf5"}}
